ActFinancial Administration Act
PrecisCERTAIN FEES RELATING TO EXPORT CERTIFICATES REMISSION ORDER - which remits a portion of the fee that exceeds $75 paid or payable for the issuance of an export certificate for live animals or embryos during the period beginning on October 1, 2008 and ending on September 30, 2009, if an accredited veterinarian provided the inspection services on which the export certificate is based. Remission would also be provided for certain fees paid or payable by IND Lifetech inc. for export certificates issued from April 1, 2007 to March 31, 2008.
